<p>I had one of these lists when I was younger and in high school and thought it was cute and Pinterest-y. But honestly, I did end up loving adding things to it and looking back on it to see old things that used to make me happy (some that still did, some that didnâ€™t anymore). I love lists. I always have. Iâ€™m glad that I brought this practice back into my life because it is a soothing act for me to make a list, and itâ€™s also a good reminder to look back on moments of happiness.</p>

